    "BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_SpenserFirstIntro": "SPENSER: My physical being is with\\nPOKéMON always!\\pMy heart beats as one with\\nPOKéMON always!\\pYoung one of a TRAINER!\\nDo you believe in your POKéMON?\\pCan you believe them through\\nand through?\\pIf your bonds of trust are frail,\\nyou will never beat my brethren!",
    "BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_ProveYourBondWithMons": "The bond you share with your POKéMON!\\nProve it to me here!",
    "BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_SpenserPostSilverBattle": "SPENSER: Gwahahah!\\pHah, you never fell for my bluster!\\nSorry for trying that stunt!\\pHere!\\nBring me the thing!",
    "BattleFrontier_BattlePalaceBattleRoom_Text_LetsSeeFrontierPass": "My, my, if only you could maintain that\\nfacade of distinguished authority…\\pHere!\\nLet's see your FRONTIER PASS!",
